	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Inquisitors specialize in hunting demons, monsters, or practitioners of dark magic. They are more focused on their enemy than on their own code of conduct, though most inquisitors are specialized paladins within a larger order, meaning that they are expected to follow the tenets of their faith. Some inquisitors are entirely independent, serving as roaming monster hunters fueled by their desire to protect the innocent. Finally, some inquisitors serve as enforcers for an organized religion. These enforcers are typically notorious outside their own religion.</p><table><caption>Inquisitor</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.QSiA5ovOgSx7yyR2]{Judgement} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.0ZGg51hvC0shFDzx]{Reveal the Enemy}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.FIy35pfzsDkO7jmK]{Aura of Revelation}</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.QSiA5ovOgSx7yyR2]{Judgement} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.0ZGg51hvC0shFDzx]{Reveal the Enemy}</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.xplieXrVfdcqxJES]{Master Seeker}</td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption>Expanded Spell List</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Paladin Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Extra Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Bd3Qt5IS1z5S4356]{Comprehend Languages}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.xxhReFO5bBzylMmY]{Faerie Fire}</em></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.YgQ8dqJ8elyPCrWf]{Detect Thoughts}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.L8vSNGiYvs5dJi64]{Zone of Truth}</em></td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.ww8DtX0ROIGyTnYj]{Clairvoyance}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.yJzrgvxa2QVSAr6z]{Tongues}</em></td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.VhcOj938RhpZDDhI]{Arcane Eye}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.ynE0kLi6F2AdqnR7]{Banishment}</em></td></tr><tr><td>17</td><td><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.piOfkIqVwkpV4Znb]{Break Enchantment}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.kj85kLkGaxNuoGKz]{Telepathic Bond}</em></td></tr></tbody></table>",
